headline: Dollar Tree Announces Leadership Changes
summary: CHESAPEAKE, Va., November 13, 2024--Dollar Tree, Inc. (NASDAQ: DLTR) today announced several updates to its executive leadership team. These strategic shifts have been implemented to further position Dollar Tree and Family Dollar for success in the future.
